# ── DB & backups ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# All SQLite files live under data/. Anything matching *.db anywhere in the
# repo is a dev artefact and must NOT be committed — there used to be a stray
# tracked tracktheticket.db at the repo root that kept getting restored on
# checkout; the broad pattern below guards against that recurring.
*.db
*.db.backup*

